T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"valuable<br />\ninvaluable"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"flammable<br />\ninflammable<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c0e6f18266f69f18d172b603121849c1755e17","tid":2365941,"uid":355310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71f1c0db8faf934d093ede1b5bee70232529553","tid":2365941,"uid":224281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"雙重否定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"睇完呢個答案，我唔認為冇人唔會唔同意完全冇可能仲係唔明嘅可能性絕對係零"},{"pid":"9266777f436bdeab10a9157bad8324cd93341bf4","tid":2365941,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc8bd1584aedeb9827fad8186f5cc7576d8bbbb","tid":2365941,"uid":48161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"839cb6238bf49822f8603d6e87f20cbfba3588b5","tid":2365941,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"valuable<br />\ninvaluable"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"flammable<br />\ninflammable<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩查左lexico，原來有解<br />\n<br />\nUsage<br />\nThe words inflammable and flammable both have the same meaning, &lsquo;easily set on fire&rsquo;. This might seem surprising, given that the prefix in- normally has a negative meaning (as in indirect and insufficient), and so it might be expected that inflammable would mean the opposite of flammable, i.e. &lsquo;not easily set on fire&rsquo;. In fact, inflammable is formed using a different Latin prefix in-, which has the meaning &lsquo;into&rsquo; and here has the effect of intensifying the meaning of the word in English. Flammable is a far commoner word than inflammable and carries less risk of confusion"},{"pid":"da6d3d9d0e96cb20ae48667588cbb46772eb4256","tid":2365941,"uid":355310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85dd9a66b452f033cb2120680a7d23cba30ddafe","tid":2365941,"uid":180401,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用法都唔同 小朋友番屋企問下大人<br />\n定係你屋企大人都唔太識廣東話？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:51:38.000Z","msg":"有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145062f77994eae341aed520f1d46ea01057cc79","tid":2365941,"uid":323720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"係咪應該係無陰功？<br />\n無陰間功德"}]}